name: Help Duke 2 come to life!
blurb: The successor to Talking Duke, a mobile game with 609,579 downloads.\nFor puppy, dog, and animal lovers.

rewards.reward: You will get an email to unlock unlimited accessories with a unique one-time access key.  Dress Duke however you want with shirts, jerseys, and props.   A link to download the free finished app.  All the previous rewards too.

We would like to personally, AND publicly, thank you kindly!  You'll have your name listed on the Super Special Page (A.K.A. "The Credits") of the Talking Duke app!  You will also be included in the fun!  You will enjoy occasional project updates from the team.
Two different cool Duke stickers.  Has your dog done a Duke?  and I like Duke!  A link to download the free finished app.  All the previous rewards too.

Signed, sealed, delivered- it's yours!\r\nYou'll receive an awesome work of art (a postcard) to send to your favorite special someone, hang on your refrigerator, or frame and place on your mantelpiece.

You can get your face and voice in the app itself.  Duke will wear your face on his shirt as he entertains and performs his tricks.  A link to download the free finished app.  All the previous rewards too.

Duke will personally thank you, calling you by name, in Duke's gravely and sophisticated voice  when you press the thank you button.  The button comes after entering your unique secret key so Duke 'knows' you.  The voice is by a professional voice actor.  A link to download the free finished app.  All the previous rewards too.

You won't want to miss out on this golden lucky Duke coin! Featuring impeccably rendered designs of Duke, flawlessly crafted, this snazzy golden disk will be your very own prestigious timeless souvenir and keepsake to carry with you as a good luck charm, or to be displayed.  A link to download the free finished app.  All the previous rewards too.
Wear your heart (and our art) on your sleeve! You will be sportin' a Talking Duke  tee shirt. Now that's stylin'.

Adorn your walls with an image of Duke and the  signatures of Cloudburst Games' design team with signatures of studio head Ron Packard, Jr.,  and the lovely and talented Ashley Mitchell (featured in our video).  A link to download the free finished app.  All the previous rewards too.

Get your own Duke baseball cap.  Cotton Twill Pro-Style Flexfit.  Fade resistant, color fast polyester blend makes this cap a great choice if you're in bright sunlight for long periods of time.  A link to download the free finished app.  All the previous rewards too.

A limited run of wonderful Duke stuffed animal/plushie.  This will be a collectable lovable stuffed-toy dog that you can hold dear and cuddle.  A link to download the free finished app.  All the previous rewards too.
Awesome travelers backpack and beer mug.  Enjoy the outdoors, with your dog and Duke!  A link to download the free finished app. All the previous rewards too.

You will have early access to the app, possibly months before its release.  You will have an opportunity to try out the new product before it is even released and give your praise and feedback directly to Cloudburst Games, and perhaps even end up influencing the development of the app itself with your input, you genius, you.  A link to download the free finished app.  All the previous rewards too.
Be listed among the photo gallery of top backers within the app in a slick display.  A link to download the free finished app. All the previous rewards too.
